<item>
            <title>[FLINK-3054] Remove R (return) type variable from SerializationSchema</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3054</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For the upcoming 1.0 release, I would like to remove the R type parameter from the &lt;tt&gt;SerializationSchema&lt;/tt&gt; class.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;DeserializationSchema&lt;/tt&gt; doesn&apos;t have a variable input type either and I think its okay to serialize and deserialize to byte[] all the time through these interfaces.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
